## SRC\_OUT\_I variable

Porter-Duff operator for packed ints. The source that does not overlap the destination replaces the destination.

[porterDuff](./porter-duff.porterduff.md)

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
SRC_OUT_I: (a: number, b: number) => number
```
